"ubuntu.com/tutorial/tutorial-install-ubuntu-desktop\" rel=\"external\" title="
"\"a tutorial on installing Ubuntu\"> zor değil </a>, ancak Windows veya "
"macOS'u tamamen silmek daha da kolay."

#: docroot/lib/views/switch_to_linux.try_or_install.php:42
